				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12164025#post-4294651</guid>
				<title>Co-author post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12164025/scp-4363#post-4294651</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2019 10:17:10 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>3146689</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <h3><span><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A0fHWOA7bq8">♪ ♪ ♪ Wake me up, I'm living a nightmare ♪ ♪ ♪</a></span></h3> </div> <hr /> <p>This was a tough one to pull off. Dunno how it'll do, but let's hope for the best. ¯\_(ツ)_/¯</p> <p>So, the second part of my team's collabcon storyline, written by me and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/arbelict" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4305778&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561894456" alt="Arbelict" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4305778)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/arbelict" >Arbelict</a></span>.</p> <p>Huge thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=634139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561894456" alt="Gene R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=634139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gene-r" >Gene R</a></span> for helping us with wording in the logs. Also to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561894456" alt="FloppyPhoenix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/floppyphoenix" >FloppyPhoenix</a></span> for her great line-by-line crit.</p> <p>Also <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5271378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561894456" alt="Mew-ltiverse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5271378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" >Mew-ltiverse</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4646198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561894456" alt="BlueJones" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4646198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" >BlueJones</a></span> took a look at this, so thanks to them too.</p> <p>Thanks to all of you for reading as well!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Images</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;There&nbsp;you&nbsp;go</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li><a href="https://pxhere.com/ru/photo/615264">https://pxhere.com/ru/photo/615264</a> - Vinyl record from the description</li> <li><a href="http://www.publicdomainfiles.com/show_file.php?id=13545193213639">http://www.publicdomainfiles.com/show_file.php?id=13545193213639</a> - The office room</li> <li><a href="https://pixnio.com/architecture/cathedrals-churches/church-religion-architecture-cathedral-facade-landmark">https://pixnio.com/architecture/cathedrals-churches/church-religion-architecture-cathedral-facade-landmark</a> - The Ruins</li> <li><a href="https://pixabay.com/ru/photos/%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA-%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%83%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B6%D0%B8%D1%82%D1%8C-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B0%D1%80-756826/">https://pixabay.com/ru/photos/%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA-%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%83%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%B6%D0%B8%D1%82%D1%8C-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B0%D1%80-756826/</a> - Firefighters</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
